Rating: 4
Wonderful! This was my first experience cooking with aubergines and it was so worth it! I deviated from the recipe as follows: No capers, so I upped the garlic to two large cloves to add flavour. I didn't have any peperoncini, so I used the pepper flakes. Oh, and I used 1 tsp oregano rather than 1/2 tsp. Delish. We took the suggestion of using them in a sandwich with crusty bread, mozzarella and prosciuto. You have to try it that way. AMAZING!

